===================================================================================================================
that time you get a very rare gun, but the look of the parts make you want to kill someone. i know this, and its sucks!

so i made this mod. remove any parts i hate (keep the efects).

if you want ther is a spot ther YOU can change the parts. all you need is to pot gibs code for the item you want to change in the first [Part ID], in the secand pot the end of the part you want it to be.
like if you have: GD_Weap_Pistol.Grip.Pistol_Grip_Vladof pot just the: Pistol_Grip_Vladof

the list:

Pistol_Grip_Vladof=Pistol_Grip_Tediore

Pistol_Grip_Maliwan=Pistol_Grip_Bandit

RL_Sight_Tediore=None

RL_Sight_Maliwan=RL_Sight_Torgue

Pistol_Sight_Vladof=Pistol_Sight_Hyperion

Pistol_Sight_Tediore=Pistol_Sight_Bandit

SG_Sight_Tediore=SG_Sight_Torgue

SG_Sight_Bandit=None

SG_Grip_Tediore=SG_Grip_Hyprerion

SG_Grip_Jakobs=SG_Grip_Bandit

Sniper_Sight_Maliwan=None

created by ozay (or oz yohay)
===================================================================================================================

set GD_Weap_Pistol.Grip.Pistol_Grip_Vladof GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName Pistol_Grip_Tediore

set GD_Weap_Pistol.Grip.Pistol_Grip_Maliwan GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName Pistol_Grip_Bandit

set GD_Weap_Launchers.Sight.RL_Sight_Tediore GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName None

set GD_Weap_Launchers.Sight.RL_Sight_Maliwan GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName RL_Sight_Torgue

set GD_Weap_Launchers.Sight.RL_Sight_Maliwan GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName L_Sight_Torgue

set GD_Weap_Pistol.Sight.Pistol_Sight_Vladof GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName Pistol_Sight_Hyperion

set GD_Weap_Pistol.Sight.Pistol_Sight_Tediore GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName Pistol_Sight_Bandit

set GD_Weap_Shotgun.Sight.SG_Sight_Tediore GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName SG_Sight_Torgue

set GD_Weap_Shotgun.Sight.SG_Sight_Bandit GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName None

set GD_Weap_Shotgun.Grip.SG_Grip_Tediore GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName SG_Grip_Hyprerion

set GD_Weap_Shotgun.Grip.SG_Grip_Jakobs GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName SG_Grip_Bandit

set GD_Weap_SniperRifles.Sight.Sniper_Sight_Maliwan GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName None

set [Part ID] GestaltModeSkeletalMeshName [Part ID]

